    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Process in which photographically produced dye images are physically transferred from a light-sensitive matrix to a receiving sheet; developed by Eastman Kodak Company and marketed with the trade names Verifax, Readyprint, and Ektalith.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000009031/Hawken Copying Methods Manual (1966)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proceso en el cual imágenes teñidas, fotográficamente producidas, son transferidas físicamente de una matriz fotosensible a una lámina receptora desarrollada por Eastman Kodak Company y comercializada con los nombres comerciales Verifax, Readyprint y Ektalith.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Proces waarbij fotografisch geproduceerde kleurenbeelden worden "overgebracht" van een lichtgevoelige matrix naar een vel fotopapier. Dit procédé is ontwikkeld door Eastman Kodak Company en op de markt gebracht onder de gedeponeerde merknamen Verifax, Readyprint en Ektalith.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>由美國伊士曼-柯達公司（Eastman Kodak Company）發明的轉印技術，將拍攝所產生的含染料影像，由感光元件轉印至相紙的過程，柯達公司以「Verifax」、「Readyprint」、「Ektalith」等名稱做為此技術的商標。
</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
